item.title: Getting your fill of Reverse Engineering and Malware Analysis
item.description: Matt, from the Exotic Liability forums, posed a suggestion for a episode: “Getting started [in] reverse engineering hardware drivers?”. I thought this was an interesting topic to attack so, I dug a bit into my RSS feed pile of goo and compiled this list of links. Hope this helps Matt. Individuals — Skywing - http://www.nynaeve.net/ Egypt - http://0xegypt.blogspot.com/ Yoni - http://blogs.msdn.com/michael_howard/ Raymond Chen - http://blogs.msdn.com/oldnewthing/
